org.vast.ogc.om

Class ObservationRef

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vast.ogc.xlink.CachedReference<GenericFeature>
      • org.vast.ogc.gml.FeatureRef
        • org.vast.ogc.om.ObservationRef
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AbstractFeature, AbstractGML, GenericFeature, IObservation, IXlinkReference<GenericFeature>

    public class ObservationRef
extends FeatureRef
implements IObservation

    Wrapper class for use when an IObservation object is or can be included by reference. This enables fetching and instantiating the target object lazily.

    Since:
    Sep 28, 2012
    Author:
    Alex Robin
